data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS. Situated within close proximity to popular shops, restaurants, schools, and the thrilling Shipwreck Island Waterpark, this three-bedroom, two-bathroom home ensures you're at the heart of it all in Panama City Beach. What truly sets it apart is its location - less than one mile away from the breathtaking Gulf of Mexico, allowing you to savor the beauty of the ocean whenever you desire. This residence is nestled in the welcoming community of Palm Cove, where you'll enjoy routine lawncare and community pools as wonderful perks! As you step inside through the main entry, you'll be greeted by an inviting open layout, complete with a vaulted ceiling and easy-to-maintain tile and laminate flooring throughout. The spacious primary bedroom includes a convenient walk-in closet, and the primary bathroom offers the luxury of a generously sized double-vanity. Whether you're seeking a personal haven or an investment opportunity, this property is the one to buy!
